<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bots" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bots,</orth> small worms found in the entrails of horses: <cit><quote>begnawn with the b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 56</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to give poor jades the b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 1, 11</bibl></cit>. Used as an execration: <cit><quote>b. on it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 2.1.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 1, 124</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>